SSO4DD.description: {"code":"sso4dd","name":"达达认证（运营平台）","desc":"达达SSO认证"}

SSO4DJ.description: {"code":"sso4dj","name":"到家认证（商家中心）","desc":"到家SSO认证"}

SSO4HB.description: {"code":"sso4hb","name":"海博认证（商家端）","desc":"海博商家端"}

ALWAYS.description: {"code":"always","name":"无限重试","desc":"允许无限重试，直到成功"}

SIMPLE.description: {"code":"simple","name":"固定次数","desc":"固定次数[maxNum]重试策略"}

TIMEOUT.description: {"code":"timeout","name":"限时重试","desc":"限定时间内重试策略[timeout],单位:秒"}

BREAK_CHECK.description: {"code":"break_check","name":"阻塞校验","desc":"前置处理器中决定当前步骤是否会执行"}

PARAM_PREPARE.description: {"code":"param_prepare","name":"数据清洗","desc":"执行上下文的参数处理"}

NO.description: {"code":"no","name":"立即重试","desc":"即当重试时是立即重试"}

FIXED.description: {"code":"fixed","name":"固定间隔","desc":"period 指定休眠时间,单位:秒"}

UNIFORM_RANDOM.description: {"code":"uniformRandom","name":"范围随机","desc":"在 [minPeriod, maxPeriod] 之间取一个随机休眠时间,单位:秒"}

EXPONENTIAL.description: {"code":"exponential","name":"指数递增","desc":"initialInterval 指定初始休眠时,maxInterval 指定最大休眠时间,multiplier 指定乘数，即下一次休眠时间为当前休眠时间 * multiplier"}

EXPONENTIAL_RANDOM.description: {"code":"exponentialRandom","name":"随机指数","desc":"引入随机乘数，之前说过固定乘数可能会引起很多服务同时重试导致 DDos，使用随机休眠时间来避免这种情况"}
